pl0-compiler
(c)by xStone 2012
released under terms of GNU General Public License v2


1. Build
----------------
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ qmake ../pl0-compiler.pro
$ make


2. Usage
----------------
pl0-compiler [ flags ] source_code_file

Flags:
-l: lex source code, and output token stream.
-p: parse token stream, and output abstract syntax tree.
-a: analytics abstract syntax tree, and output pcode.
-e: execute pcode.
-?: help.
